graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	appHealthGetTechnicalSolutions (query: $query)
	{
		id
		customerName
		name
		description
		architectureDiagram
		proposal
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	appHealthFindTechnicalSolution (query: $query)
	{
		id
		customerName
		name
		description
		architectureDiagram
		proposal
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	appHealthFindTechnicalSolutionById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		customerName
		name
		description
		architectureDiagram
		proposal
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:AppHealthUpdateTechnicalSolutionInput!)
{
	appHealthUpdateTechnicalSolution (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		customerName
		name
		description
		architectureDiagram
		proposal
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	appHealthDeleteTechnicalSolutionById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		customerName
		name
		description
		architectureDiagram
		proposal
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	appHealthDeleteTechnicalSolutions (query: $query)
	{
		id
		customerName
		name
		description
		architectureDiagram
		proposal
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
